body:
TS7 Merch

I see a lot of people posting and complaining about the drip marketing @taylornation is doing with the merch this era. Personally, I don’t get it. I’m absolutely loving the excitement every day of seeing what’s next. I’ve also been going through somewhat of a rough patch in my life, and getting these little surprises every day has given me some happiness in my life ♥️

summary: I absolutely hate that this is happening!!  I live in the Netherlands so when this cd came online it was 2 in the night And I...
body: I absolutely hate that this is happening!! I live in the Netherlands so when this cd came online it was 2 in the night And I was asleep. By the time I saw you could buy these they were already sold out. And now people are selling them for a ridiculous amount of money. To these people I just want to say: What kind of person would want to do this to true fans? Do you feel good about making money this way? It’s just sad this is happening…. I am sorry for the negativity But I am just not ok with this… 😕😕😕
